	THE LIST OF OPERATORS IN C
       ''''''''''''''''''''''''''''
A- Airthmatic Operator: Perfrom simple airthmatic operations.

	 SYMBOLS	-	Description

	    +			Add
	    -			Subtract
	    *			Multiply 
	    /                   Divide
            %			Modulus
	   ++			Increment
	   -- 			Decrement


B- Relational Operators: Tests value for equality.
	
	SYMBOLS		-	DEscription
	   
	  ==			Equal
	  !=			Not equal
	  >			Greater than
	  <			Smaller than
	  >=			Greater than equal
	  <=			Less than equal


C-Logical operators: Tests logic
	
	SYMBOL		-	Description

	  &			Bitwise and
	  |			Bitwise or
	  ^			Bitwise xor
	  ~			Bitwise One's Compliment
	  <<			Bitwise Shift left
	  >>			Bitwise Shift Right


D- Assignment Operators: Assign expression to varaibles.

	SYMBOL         -        Description

	  =			Assign eqaul
	  +=			Assign plus equal
	  -=                    Assign minus equal
	  *= 			Assign multiply equal
	  /= 			Assign Divide equal
	  %=			Assign Modulo equal
	 <<=			Assign right shift equal
	 >>=			Assign left shift equal
	  &=			Assign and equal
	  |=			Assign Or equal
	  ^=			Assign Xor equal


E- Data Operators: Deals with elements of Data structure in C


	Operators 		Description
	
	sizeof()		Get the size of
	[]			Array subscript
	& 			The address of
	*			The value of
	->			Structure dereference
	.			Structure reference



SOME OTHER COMMON SYMBOLS AND OPERATORS
	
	,			Comma
	()			Paraentheses
	{}			Braces
	:			COlon
	//			Single line comment
	/*			Multi line comment opening
	*/			Multi line comment ending



Conditional Operator: (exp1 ? exp2:exp3)


NOTE- PRECIDENCY : Airthmatic > Relational > Logical







